Anton Lesser https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anton_Lesser 0 Anton Lesser (born 14 February 1952) is an English actor. He is particularly well known for his roles as Qyburn in the HBO series Game of Thrones, as Thomas More in Wolf Hall, as Harold Macmillan in The Crown, and as Chief Superintendent Bright in the Inspector Morse spin-off, Endeavour.
